io.netty.channel.aio

Class AbstractAioChannel

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.netty.util.DefaultAttributeMap
      • io.netty.channel.AbstractChannel
        • io.netty.channel.aio.AbstractAioChannel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Channel, AttributeMap, Comparable<Channel>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AioServerSocketChannel, AioSocketChannel

    public abstract class AbstractAioChannel
extends AbstractChannel
    Abstract base class for Channel implementations that use the new AsynchronousChannel which is part of NIO.2.
